    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>allspice </strong>to the pan and cook for 2 min</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and a couple of splashes of <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 10-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1148.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
