            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Separate 4 <span class=\"text-purple\">[6]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span><strong> leaves</strong> from the<strong> lettuce</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>inner core[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1148.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1148.-step-5-x400.jpg",
