            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Once pulled, mix the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> in with the pan juices – this is your <strong>shredded fiery chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1148.-step-7-x200.jpg",
