          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1148.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1148.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> ciabattas</strong> in half</p><p>Assemble each ciabatta with a<strong> lettuce leaf</strong>,<strong> a cheesy pineapple slice</strong>,<strong> the shredded fiery chicken</strong>, another<strong> lettuce leaf</strong>, another<strong> cheesy pineapple slice</strong> and finally with a dollop of <strong>pineapple mayo</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> on the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
